    <section id="timeline" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Application Timeline</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Week 1-2</div>
          <div class="flex-grow bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Initial Setup & Planning</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">
              Engage local legal/accounting firm. Determine business structure (100% foreign, JV, or capital
              contribution). Identify registered office address. Prepare documentation including notarized passport
              copies and business plan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Week 2-4</div>
          <div class="flex-grow bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Investment Registration Certificate (IRC)</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">
              Submit application to Department of Planning and Investment. Include project proposal, proof of
              funds, lease agreement for office. Processing time: 15-30 working days. Some industries require
              additional ministry approvals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Week 4-6</div>
          <div class="flex-grow bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Enterprise Registration Certificate (ERC)</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">
              After IRC approval, apply for ERC (business license). Processing: 3-5 working days. Receive company
              seal and tax registration. Open corporate bank account and deposit charter capital (within 90 days).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Week 6-8</div>
          <div class="flex-grow bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Investor Visa Application</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">
              With IRC and ERC in hand, apply for ĐT (investor) visa at Immigration Department. Submit proof of
              capital contribution. Processing: 5-10 working days. Can apply from within Vietnam (if on valid visa)
              or from Vietnamese embassy abroad.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Week 8-12</div>
          <div class="flex-grow bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Visa Issuance & Registration</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">
              Receive investor visa (1-5 years depending on IRC duration). Register temporary residence at local
              police station within 24 hours. Begin business operations. Apply for Temporary Residence Card (TRC)
              for multi-entry convenience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

